dct_title_s: Greece at the time of the Persian Wars
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. At head of map: [Dr. William Smith's Ancient atlas]. 21. Plate 21 from: Atlas of ancient geography, biblical and classical ... / edited by William Smith and George Grove. London : J. Murray, 1874. Historic Maps copy imperfect: Upper margin of map wanting, with lost of text. Text at head of map suggested by plate 20.
